    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A type of tin brass that is widely used for products requiring high strength and a high level of corrosion resistance, particularly marine equipment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
